title: LFT for SS February Premade 5v5 Tournament
body:
**S7: platinum 2**. I main **fizz mid**, Secondarily: **fiddlesticks/kha'zix jungle**.
Have reached plat since preseason 6.
Have played LoL since S2.
I_ have mic and discord _and I'm _willing to be a cooperative team player_.

Open premade 5v5 tournament on February 10, and February 11:
https://battlefy.com/summonerssociety/summoners-society-february-premade-5v5/5a0fae5aa5eadf0356860093/info?infoTab=details 

Please add me on LoL and message me, or comment below if you are interested in having me on your team.
